  ((SELECT id FROM mock_test_bank WHERE exam_type = 'TOPIK_II' AND test_number = 36 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1), 'listening', 37, '여자 :대표님은 ‘날씨 경영인’이라고 알려져 있는데요.조금 생소한 말입
