  ((SELECT id FROM mock_test_bank WHERE exam_type = 'TOPIK_II' AND test_number = 36 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1), 'reading', 80, '인간은 ( )중심으로 세상일을 받아들인다.연인과
